/SCD/XXERASH/XX. We must study the Torah with a view toward discerning the great
traits of Jewish consciousness that struggled to become articulate in its tra-
ditions, laws, prophecies, psalms and wisdom. We should study all of its
traditions with the purpose of finding out their bearing on IsraelÚs destiny
and duty in the world and then seek to make that destiny and duty our
own.    /SC/XXM.M.K. (ADAPTED)/XX/PR
/PR
